query:
select distinct ?name
where 
{
   ?name dbpedia-owl:director dbpedia:Woody_Allen.
   ?name dbpedia-owl:writer dbpedia:Woody_Allen.
   ?name dbpedia-owl:starring dbpedia:Woody_Allen.
}

select distinct ?name
where 
{
   ?name dbpedia-owl:director dbpedia:Woody_Allen.
   ?name dbpedia-owl:writer dbpedia:Woody_Allen.
   ?name dbpedia-owl:starring dbpedia:Woody_Allen.
  
}

select ?name
where 
{ ?name dbpedia-owl:director dbpedia:Woody_Allen
 
}

select ?name 
where 

{ 
?name dbpedia-owl:director dbpedia:Woody_Allen.
   ?name dbpedia-owl:writer dbpedia:Woody_Allen.
    ?name dbpedia-owl:starring dbpedia:Woody_Allen.
  
}

select ?name 
where 

{ 
    ?name dbpedia-owl:director dbpedia:Woody_Allen.
    ?x dbpedia-owl:writer dbpedia:Woody_Allen.
    ?y dbpedia-owl:starring dbpedia:Woody_Allen.
FILTER(?name=?x=?y).
  
}

select ?name 
where 

{ 
    ?name dbpedia-owl:director dbpedia:Woody_Allen.
    ?x dbpedia-owl:writer dbpedia:Woody_Allen.
    ?y dbpedia-owl:starring dbpedia:Woody_Allen.
   FILTER(?name = ?x = ?y).
  
}

select ?m
where 

{ 
    ?name dbpedia-owl:director dbpedia:Woody_Allen.
    ?x dbpedia-owl:writer dbpedia:Woody_Allen.
    ?y dbpedia-owl:starring dbpedia:Woody_Allen.
   FILTER(?name = ?x = ?y =?m).
  
}

select ?godina,?kuka,?naslov
where
{
  dbpedia:The_Little_Prince dbpprop:titleOrig ?naslov.
dbpprop:releaseDate ?godina.
dbpprop:publisher ?kuka.



}

select  ?godina
where
{
  dbpedia:The_Little_Prince 
dbpprop:releaseDate ?godina.





}
limit 1

select ?x
where
{
  ?album dbpedia-owl:artist dbpedia:Depeche_Mode.
  ?a dbpprop:title ?x.
filter(?album=?a).

}
